issue.title: resize video
issue.body: Currently if the video gets resized it doesn't always update the blue UI element that indicates where the ads are.

issue.title: Create annotator extension
issue.body: Create extension that allows users to submit time regions that are embedded ads. They would then be connected to the English captions to annotate positive chunks, and automatically set all others to be negative.

issue.title: Change the name of classify.py to be generate_ground_truth.py
Create trainer
issue.body:
Create trainer. 

The trainer assumes a dataset that looks like 

timing, token, yes/no

Concat the token's word vector with the percentage-completed of the video (token start time / total video time). 


Try: 

* Linear SVM 

* Logistic Regression 

* (Later) Keras BiLSTM + Dense layer
